&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;18q50h3&quot; data-start=&quot;2036&quot; data-end=&quot;2218&quot;&gt;Own dynamic testing from start to finish, including pre-test analysis, test planning, sensor selection, instrumentation, setup, execution, data processing, and post-test reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
